                <note rend="inline" type="source">763.72119/6723: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the <gloss type="to">Commission to Negotiate Peace</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1919-09-16T15:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 16, 1919, 3 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>3139. Your urgent 4197, September 13. After consultation with Hoover and Dulles,
                    the Department approves the second line of action mentioned in your
                    telegram.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Phillips</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
